profile:
ROCO PRO LTD provides full basement finish renovation service. 
We are here to help you with any project big or small. Being it a finished basement or a more complex second unit. 
We will guide you through: city permit application for basement renovation, finding the best basement layout and selecting the finishes. 
ROCO PRO is committed to build a place that you will enjoy and be proud of.

We have our own in house framing, drywall and patching team.
Plumbing and Electrical are subcontracted to licensed trade professionals. 

ROCO PRO Basement Finishing, Basement Renovation, Basement Legal Unit, Finished Basement, Basement Second Unit
